  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.gson.JsonDeserializer<ArrayList<ImageProperty>>

    public class LegacyImageViewProcessor
extends ViewProcessor<ArrayList<ImageProperty>>
    Migration class to allow for converting old ImageProperty class structure to new.
    Register this in your UiSettings.Builder by using the following code 
    registerType(new TypeToken>(){}.getType(), new LegacyImageViewProcessor())
